[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man suffers serious head injury in Londonderry attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man in his 50s has been taken to hospital after suffering a serious head injury in an attack in Londonderry.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Police said he was assaulted shortly before 06:30 BST on Monday.
It happened in Bloomfield Park.
They have appealed for any witnesses to come forward.
